00:02:27.233 --> 00:02:28.633
and the other is EGCG.

00:02:28.666 --> 00:02:29.333
Here,

00:02:29.333 --> 00:02:30.533
I must talk about

00:02:30.533 --> 00:02:32.833
the additional properties of the ingredient itself.

00:02:32.933 --> 00:02:35.233
In addition to its whitening

00:02:35.233 --> 00:02:36.666
and anti-sugar properties,

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:39.833
niacinamide also has an attribute of oil control.

00:02:39.833 --> 00:02:40.633
That is to say,

00:02:40.633 --> 00:02:42.800
if you If you have extremely dry skin,

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:45.000
try not to use niacinamide

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.900
because it will make your skin drier

00:02:46.900 --> 00:02:48.800
and the barrier function worse.

00:02:48.900 --> 00:02:50.600
As for niacinamide products,

00:02:50.600 --> 00:02:51.600
the more classic

